HEADWORD: Orderer
<hw>Or"der*er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>One who
puts in order, arranges, methodizes, or regulates.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>One who gives orders.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Ordering</ent>⟦br⟧
